From 87926da8e1b920bfa9da4c94579bdb498f5b939f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ramanathan Choodamani <rchoodam@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Thu, 17 Jul 2025 00:56:39 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL:hostapd: Add support to receive and process
 MSCS event from driver

Add support to receive the MSCS flow event from driver with the
flow_info that needs to be programmed to the network for DL
classification

Patch-dependency: r89-09-UPSTREAM-hostapd-MSCS-Add-protocol-support-for-mscs.patch
Patch-work: NA
Tag: MSCS

Signed-off-by: Ramanathan Choodamani <rchoodam@qti.qualcomm.com>
